				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-qu%C3%A1-M%E1%BA%A1nh-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%A0o-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-ch%E1%BB%A7-b%E1%BA%A1-huynh-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-N50q6f-0icrKz_EiERi1sQ">Cửu nguyệt nhất nhật quá Mạnh thập nhị tào trưởng, thập tứ chủ bạ huynh đệ - 九月一日過孟十二倉曹、十四主簿兄弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C4%A9-Ng%E1%BA%A1c/D%E1%BA%A1-th%C3%ADnh-t%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-e_6bwyayRmrBY1wDpWEuYQ">Dạ thính tỳ bà kỳ 3 - 夜聽琵琶其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C4%A9-Ng%E1%BA%A1c/author-MBBxHkvjtyblFe5zp-xIkw">Dương Sĩ Ngạc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Ho%C3%A0n-c%E1%BB%B1u-c%C6%B0/poem-0oFKaz2ft1632fKqcqg2sg">Hoàn cựu cư - 還舊居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Minh-Phi-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-XvTLEEj12j7qyu3L3kpuqA">Minh Phi khúc kỳ 2 - 明妃曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/Quan-Chu-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%C3%BA/poem-t5SDq6ooOoPLPyHT8hFmCg">Quan Chu nhạc phú - 觀周樂賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-TDh6Z0N6kQIoYYwYA3fCGw">Nguyễn Nhữ Bật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%E1%BB%9F-ki%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7zX_fvrqSHORA8aiuARZQw">Sở kiến hành - 所見行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>